title: This Situation Makes Me So Mad...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the viral plane lady and the weird theories that have followed after this incident. The Internet always succeeds in lowering my expectations for human intelligence and I wanted to talk about one theory that I can provide a lot of context and understanding too. Thanks for watching!
